additional_info:
V. 1.0 Just the Spielen zone; access to game tables.

V. 1.1 (27 January 2018) Just the Spielen zone; added the tables itself, everything in background removed and colored in black except for the avatars, the logo, the chat and the names of the players.

-V 1.2 (27 January 2018) Just the Spielen zone; I have modified the code so the table itself, only the table and not the background appears now so it is less ugly. The code it is .tricks so if you want it "painted black" just modify:

.tricks{
   
       background-color: black !important;

}

css:
@-moz-document url-prefix("https://www.sauspiel.de/schafkopf/spielen") {
/*colors and background in general*/
.table-list, .chat__messages, .chat__textarea, .user-list, .participant-box__user{
	
	background-color: black !important;
	
}

li.table-list-item.table-list-item_full, .table-list-item, .table-list-item__btn-icon, div#data-reactid{
	
	background-color: black !important
}
											
.chat__item_link{
	
    color: #f60000 !important;
											
}

.user_participant-box  {
    
    background-color: #2b7e2e !important;
    
}

.user__name {
	
	color: #18FF00 !important;
	
}

.user__info, .user__username {
    
    background-color: black !important;
}

.user-list__item {
	
	background-color: black !important;
											
}

.room-switcher, .welcome-message, .lobby {
    
    background-image: linear-gradient(#2b4b12,#0a5423)!important;
	
}

/*images on background on gametable*/
.tricks{
	
    backface-visibility: visible !important;

}

.table{
	
	background: black !important;
	
}

.table-view{
	
	background: black !important;
	
}


.asset_floor{
	
    background: black !important;
}

.viewport_3d.viewport_table .asset_wall{
	
    background: black !important;
}
}
